  ('optometrist-moex-00774', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-aa93ddf5', 'sub-optometrist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', 'MNREAD視力表為一檢測閱讀表現的視力表，下列何者不是MNREAD視力表主要測試的項目？', '["能讀取的最小字體", "最佳閱讀速度", "能持續使用最佳閱讀速度的最小字體", "能理解前後文意的反應時間"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "72f1572c0ce9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "02767dd8f195", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1005", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "低視力學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
